00:32:27.100 --> 00:32:31.270
and then maybe 10% or 20%
we'll manage more tactically.

00:32:31.270 --> 00:32:34.090
That will also be
rules-based, but that's

00:32:34.090 --> 00:32:36.220
going to be a function of trend.

00:32:36.220 --> 00:32:38.790
And again, we don't have to
