00:50:39.810 --> 00:50:42.310
So they don't want us going on
talking about a stock trading

00:50:42.310 --> 00:50:45.130
on the pink sheets
that could double

00:50:45.130 --> 00:50:47.530
based on a mention on TV.

00:50:47.530 --> 00:50:49.930
So if you watch a show, most
of what we're talking about

00:50:49.930 --> 00:50:52.390
