00:51:07.000 --> 00:51:10.900
Just like when you watch
political news or sports news,

00:51:10.900 --> 00:51:15.100
there are some people who are
stating a fact as a reporter,

00:51:15.100 --> 00:51:17.184
and then there are people
who are on the fact.

00:51:17.184 --> 00:51:19.600
And I think keeping those two
things separate in your mind

00:51:19.600 --> 00:51:21.070
is probably the
best thing you can

00:51:21.070 --> 00:51:23.830
do when you encounter
any kind of news program,

00:51:23.830 --> 00:51:25.316
